Title: LA Times, Mon, Apr 14, 2014
Author: Sean Dobbin & the CHSVT Cruciverbalism Class / Ed. Rich Norris
Copyright: © 2014 Tribune Content Agency, LLC
Date: 2014-04-14
Notes: Sean Dobbin is an English teacher at the Community High School of Vermont (CHSVT) in St. Johnsbury. His cruciverbalism class, for which students earn fractional credit, involves vocabulary, writing, and other areas of English. 12 students worked with Mr. Dobbin on today's puzzle.


